data.description: Offering an ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE with an incredible interest rate of 5.375%! Tucked away in a private cul-de-sac off of Fairway Drive, you will find this stunning, brick ranch, boasting three bedrooms, and three bathrooms, providing plenty of room for you and your loved ones. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an open floor plan that seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The high vaulted ceilings in the living area add to the sense of space and grandeur, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere for entertaining guests or simply relaxing with your family. One of the highlights of this property is its unique location on Carroll Meadows Golf Course. Imagine waking up to the picturesque views of the lush green fairways, as the course can be admired right from your back patio. Whether you're an avid golfer or simply appreciate the serene beauty of the grounds, this location offers an idyllic retreat right in your own backyard. This home also features geothermal heating, providing an eco-friendly and efficient heating solution. With a 2-car attached garage, you'll have plenty of space to store your vehicles and outdoor equipment. Recently painted throughout, this residence showcases a fresh and modern aesthetic. Additionally, the basement has been waterproofed and warrantied, offering peace of mind. Don't miss the opportunity to make this home yours. Schedule a showing today and experience the elegance, and natural beauty that this property has to offer.
